HEADWORD: Extraversion
<hw>Ex`tra*ver"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>extra-</ets> + L. <ets>vertere</ets>, <ets>versum</ets>, to turn:
cf. F. <ets>extraversion</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act of throwing out; the
state of being turned or thrown out.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Boyle.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
